author: CNN
description: CNN's Gabe Cohen spoke to neighbors of National Guard member Andrew Wolfe who was shot in the Farragut Square Metro Station shooting in Washington, DC.
title: CNN speaks to the neighbors of DC shooting victim

author: CNN
description: Eyewitness video from Tai Po shows the fire intensifying at rapid speed as smoke pours from the high-rise. #hongkongfire #cnn
title: Blaze Engulfs Wang Fuk Court Towers Within Minutes

author: CNN
description: Afghans who fled Taliban rule say Trump’s vow to re-examine everyone brought to the U.S. under Biden has left their communities terrified of being targeted or deported. Tens of thousands still waiting for visas abroad now face a sudden freeze on Afghan immigration.
title: Afghans in the U.S. Fear Fallout After Trump Calls for New Vetting

author: CNN
description: The suspect in the shooting of two National Guard members previously worked in Afghanistan with the US government, including the CIA, CIA Director John Ratcliffe said in a statement. Rahmanullah Lakanwal, who allegedly opened fire on two West Virginia National Guard members in Washington, DC, had served as an Afghan partner to the CIA in Kandahar, Ratcliffe said in a statement to Fox News Digital yesterday.  #CNN #News
title: DC shooting suspect worked with CIA in Afghanistan

author: CNN
description: CNN correspondents turned out at parades across the country for Thanksgiving celebrations. They dressed up in fun costumes to get in the holiday spirit.
title: CNN joins Thanksgiving festivities

author: CNN
description: In a rare and wide-ranging exclusive interview with CNN’s Isa Soares, Colombian President Gustavo Petro discussed rising tensions along the coast of its neighbor Venezuela as the United States continues to ramp up military activity in the region. Petro also addressed accusations that cocaine production in Colombia has exploded under his administration and the fraught relationship he has with US President Donald Trump. #CNN #News
title: Exclusive: Colombian president says oil - not drugs - ‘at the heart of’ US pressure on Venezuela

author: CNN
description: CNN's Brian Todd reports from Farragut West Metro Station, where the Washington, DC National Guard shooting occurred. The scene had traces left of the shooting, including bullet holes in planters.
title: CNN reports from the scene of the DC National Guard shooting

author: CNN
description: The CNN Creators discuss the pros and cons of AI: the environmental impact of data centers versus how the technology is being used to help scientists save endangered species.  #CNN #News
title: CNN CREATORS (EPISODE 5): AI and the environment

author: CNN
description: This TikToker is actually trying to get his phone stolen in London. Last year, British police reported a record breaking 80,000 phones stolen in the capital. #CNN #News
title: Trying to get a phone stolen in London

author: CNN
title: Arsène Wenger speaks to CNN about Arsenal’s title hopes

author: CNN
description: 20-year-old Sarah Beckstrom and 24-year-old Andrew Wolfe, the two National Guard members who were shot in Washington, DC, were “sworn in” just 24 hours before they were shot, according to DC US Attorney Jeanine Pirro. The alleged gunman will be charged with three counts of assault with intent to kill while armed and possession of a firearm during a crime of violence, Pirro said.
title: Pirro: National Guard victims were sworn in day before they were shot

author: CNN
description: Israeli authorities stormed a theater in East Jerusalem where Palestinian children were preparing to perform a musical event, leaving them frightened and shaken. Israeli police told CNN it was enforcing a law controlling activity of the Palestinian Authority, but the Jerusalemite Youth Cultural Forum said it had no ties to the PA. CNN's Nic Robertson speaks to the children days after the raid. #cnn #news
title: Palestinian children undeterred after Israeli raid

author: CNN
description: No matter how tasty they look or how good they smell this food cannot be eaten. We took a look at the internet's obsession with hyper-realistic food candles.
title: These candles look like real food

author: CNN
description: DC US Attorney Jeanine Pirro identified the victims of yesterday’s shooting as a 20-year-old Sarah Beckstrom and 24-year-old Andrew Wolfe. Both are members of the West Virginia National Guard who were deployed in DC. The suspect has also been identified as Rahmanullah Lakanwal, an Afghan national who came to the US in 2021 under Operation Allies Welcome and was granted asylum in April. #CNN #News
title: DC US Attorney identifies 2 Nat'l guardsmen and shooter in news conference update

author: CNN
description: Witchcraft, Wicca and Paganism are more popular than ever, with some estimates topping 2 million practitioners in the US. CNN’s Donie O'Sullivan met with modern witches to discover what they've found in witchcraft that they haven't elsewhere. Stream the full story and watch more "Devoted" with Donie O'Sullivan at CNN.com/allaccess #cnn #witchcraft
title: The witch store owner fighting for religious freedom

author: CNN
description: Pope Leo has landed in Turkey, the first stop on his first trip abroad. CNN's Christopher Lamb travelled with the Pope and explains the significance of this trip. #cnn #popeleo #turkey
title: Why Pope Leo's first trip is a big deal

author: CNN
description: CNN’s Hanako Montgomery reports from the ground in Hong Kong as rescuers search for hundreds of missing people after a deadly fire raced through several high-rise buildings in an apartment complex. #CNN #News
title: Dozens killed, nearly 300 missing in Hong Kong fire

author: CNN
description: Pope Leo celebrated Thanksgiving onboard a flight to Turkey during his first international trip as Pope. He was given two pumpkin pies from journalists. CNN Vatican Correspondent Christopher Lamb reports from onboard. #CNN #news
title: Pope Leo celebrates Thanksgiving with mid-flight pumpkin pie

author: CNN
description: President Donald Trump has asked for 500 more National Guard troops to be deployed to DC in the wake of the shooting of two West Virginia National Guard members, even as the legal battle over the original deployment continues. The Trump administration has also stopped processing all immigration cases related to Afghan immigrants “indefinitely pending further review.”  #CNN #News
title: Trump vows immigration crackdown after DC National Guard shooting

author: CNN
description: After a huge fire broke out in Hong Kong’s Wang Fuk Court, debates arose about the safety of bamboo scaffolding. CNN's Karina Tsui has more from the scene of the fire. #CNN #news
title: Hong Kong fire renews debate on bamboo scaffolding

author: CNN
description:
Will an uncertain economy lead to less charitable giving this holiday season? And what if you want to give back but don’t have a lot of money? Audie talks with Sara Herschander, who covers philanthropy for @Vox’s Future Perfect, about all the ways you can help.

Listen to the full episode of CNN's The Assignment podcast: http://swap.fm/l/tawacyt112725

#cnn #news #philanthropy #giving #holidays #holidaygiving #generosity
title: Putting the “giving” back in Thanksgiving | The Assignment

author: CNN
description: Roasted turkey has long been the centerpiece of presidential Thanksgiving tables, but side dishes have evolved along with changing American tastes. CNN’s Betsy Klein explores the history of Thanksgiving dinners at the White House, including a look at molded fruit salad, a favorite featured on President Harry S. Truman’s menu.
title: See the history of White House Thanksgiving dinners

author: CNN
description: CNN’s Elex Michaelson shares what we know so far about the suspect in the shooting of two West Virginia National Guardsmen in Washington DC. #cnn #dcshooting
title: What we know about DC shooting suspect

author: CNN
description: CNN’s Hanako Montgomery breaks down the timeline of how a small fire in Hong Kong spread from one building to several in a public housing complex, leaving hundreds displaced and missing.  #cnn #news #hongkong
title: Hong Kong fire displaces hundreds into shelters like this

author: CNN
description: After a wildfire destroyed much of the Pacific Palisades neighborhood in January, one image among the devastation went global: a vintage VW bus that had somehow survived the most destructive fire in the history of Los Angeles. CNN’s Nick Watt visits the iconic vehicle at the LA Auto Show.  #palisadesfire #vw #cnn
title: Retro VW bus that stunned the Internet now fully restored

author: CNN
description: President Donald Trump condemned the shooting of two West Virginia National Guardsmen in Washington DC as a “heinous assault” and “an act of evil, an act of hatred and an act of terror.”
title: Trump responds to shooting of National Guardsmen

author: CNN
description: Thousands of residents have been displaced after deadly high-rise apartment fires in Hong Kong, which claimed dozens of lives and left hundreds missing. Rescue efforts are continuing throughout the morning as emergency teams search for survivors. #cnn #news #hongkong
title: ‘I’m devastated’: Hong Kong fire victim shares fear and confusion

author: CNN
description: Eyewitnesses recounted the violence, with one telling the WUSA local television station that they heard five shots ring out before they saw people running. Another witness, who is visiting DC for the holiday, said he hid behind chairs in Farragut Square and that he saw a person with his hands behind his back on his stomach, who he assumes was the shooter. #CNN #News
title: 'His face was covered in blood': Hear eyewitness accounts of the Nat'l Guardsmen 'targeted shooting'

author: CNN
description: Joyce Nakamura Okazaki was just seven years old when she and her family were forced to board a train in April 1942 and held at one of the US's prison camps for Japanese Americans. CNN's Stephanie Elam reports from Manzanar, California, the site of one of the prison camps, which closed 80 years ago.
title: Japanese American recalls being held at prison camp 83 years ago

author: CNN
description: Wanda Dench accidentally texted Jamal Hinton to join her Thanksgiving dinner ten years ago but doubled down on the invitation, knowing it was a mistake. Hinton showed up to her house for a plate of turkey, and this year, they celebrate ten years of Thanksgivings together.
title: How an accidental text resulted in 10 Thanksgivings together
